}

<main>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-12">
			<h1 class="text-body-emphasis outfit">Skip the Waiting Room – Get a Doctor at Your Doorstep</h1>
			<p class="fs-5"><b>Launching Soon!</b> Be among the first to experience the future of healthcare</p>
			<p class="pb-3">
				Endless waits, hectic traffic, and crowded hospitals? Healthcare shouldn’t be this hard! CuraGo brings trusted doctors–including specialists and super-specialists–right to your home for convenient, high-quality care.
			</p>
