						<li class="pb-3"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-success"></i>&nbsp; Parents managing little ones at home</li>
						<li><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-success"></i>&nbsp; Seniors or anyone with mobility challenges</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="col-md-6">
					<ul class="list-unstyled">
						<li class="pb-3"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-success"></i>&nbsp; Patients recovering from surgery who need follow-up care</li>
						<li class="pb-3"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-success"></i>&nbsp; Those needing physiotherapy in the comfort of their home</li>
