				<li class="pb-3"><i class="fa-solid fa-square-check text-success"></i>&nbsp; Eliminating long waits, stressful commutes, and hospital hassles</li>
				<li><i class="fa-solid fa-square-check text-success"></i>&nbsp; Ensuring expert care reaches you—whenever & wherever you need it</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-6">
