	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-12">
			<h3 class="text-body-emphasis outfit pb-3"><img src="~/images/about.png" alt="about us" height="50px" width="50px"> About Us</h3>
			<p>
				At CuraGo, we are reimagining and revolutionizing healthcare by making expert medical care accessible from the comfort of your home. No waiting, no hassle—just top-quality healthcare, delivered to you.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-6">
		</div>
	</div>

